== 製作 ==
小說的首個電影改編由[[焦點影業|焦點影業]]、Michael De Luca Productions及Trigger Street Productions製作<ref name=deadline201203>{{cite web|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/03/universal-pictures-and-focus-features-win-50-shades-of-grey/|title=Universal Pictures and Focus Features win ''Fifty Shades of Grey''|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|publisher=[[PMC_(company)|PMC]]|date=2012-03-26|accessdate=2012-05-07|archive-date=2014-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703044828/http://www.deadline.com/2012/03/universal-pictures-and-focus-features-win-50-shades-of-grey/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，聯同[[環球影業|環球影業]]及焦點影業於2012年3月落實了三部曲的改編權利<ref name=deadline201203/>。環球影業也是電影的分銷商，2014年3月，第一輯電影的製片人丹娜·布鲁奈蒂（Dana Brunetti）說，截至那時也還未有落實製作續集的計劃<ref>{{cite web |first=Rebecka |last=Schumann |title='Fifty Shades Darker' Movie Rumors: '50 Shades Of Grey' Producer Talks Possible Sequel |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/fifty-shades-darker-movie-rumors-50-shades-grey-producer-talks-possible-sequel-1560391 |work=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]] |accessdate=2014-06-30 |date=2014-03-10 |archive-date=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811094433/http://www.ibtimes.com/fifty-shades-darker-movie-rumors-50-shades-grey-producer-talks-possible-sequel-1560391 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第一部改編成為電影《[[格雷的五十道陰影_(電影)|格雷的五十道陰影]]》於2015年2月13日上映。在第一輯電影首映前，影迷對電影的有相當高的期望。在首部電影於2月6日在[[紐約市|紐約市]]進行特別粉絲首映後，導演{{link-en|森·泰勒·約翰遜|Sam Taylor-Johnson}}宣布，這本書續集《格雷的五十道陰影：束縛》及《[[格雷的五十道陰影：自由_(電影)|格雷的五十道陰影：自由]]》也將會改編成電影，首輯於2016年上映<ref name="sequels">{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/fifty-shades-grey-sequels-confirmed-fans-react-fifty-shades-darker-fifty-shades-freed-1807934|title='Fifty Shades of Grey' Sequels Confirmed; Fans React To 'Fifty Shades Darker' And 'Fifty Shades Freed' Movie Announcement|last=Schumann|first=Rebecka|date=2015-02-06|accessdate=2015-02-06|publisher=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|archive-date=2016-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161015195829/http://www.ibtimes.com/fifty-shades-grey-sequels-confirmed-fans-react-fifty-shades-darker-fifty-shades-freed-1807934|dead-url=no}}</ref>。就在公告之後，導演向《[[數碼間諜|數碼間諜]]》稱：「這不是我的決定，我沒有參與任何討論。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Dibdin|first1=Emma|title=Sam Taylor-Johnson on 50 Shades of Grey sequel: 'It's not my decision'|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a628865/sam-taylor-johnson-on-50-shades-of-grey-sequel-its-not-my-decision.html#~p4qeH7VPV21ieF|accessdate=2015-02-16|publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|date=2015-02-13|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216095434/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a628865/sam-taylor-johnson-on-50-shades-of-grey-sequel-its-not-my-decision.html#~p4qeH7VPV21ieF|dead-url=no}}</ref>」

2016年1月28日，導演{{link-en|森·泰勒·約翰遜|Sam Taylor-Johnson}}正式離開了專營權<ref>{{cite news|last1=Busch|first1=Anita|last2=Fleming Jr|first2=Mike|script-title=en:‘Fifty Shades Of Grey’ Director Sam Taylor-Johnson Formally Splits From Franchise|url=http://deadline.com/2015/03/fifty-shades-of-grey-sam-taylor-johnson-exits-sequel-1201393459/|accessdate=2015-04-05|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-03-25|archive-date=2015-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405013631/http://deadline.com/2015/03/fifty-shades-of-grey-sam-taylor-johnson-exits-sequel-1201393459/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月2日，《死線》確認指Michael De Luca Productions離開了[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼影業]]返回環球影業以製作《格雷的五十道陰影》的續集<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|script-title=en:The Rumors Were True: Mike De Luca Leaves Sony To Produce ‘Fifty Shades’ Sequels|url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/michael-deluca-fifty-shades-of-grey-sony-pictures-1201403872/|accessdate=2015-04-05|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-04-02|archive-date=2015-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405013535/http://deadline.com/2015/04/michael-deluca-fifty-shades-of-grey-sony-pictures-1201403872/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。製作公司後來透露，森·泰勒·約翰遜將不會為續集執導<ref name=goodbyesam>{{cite web|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|script-title=en:Sam Taylor-Johnson Will Not Direct ‘Fifty Shades Darker’|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/sam-taylor-johnson-fifty-shades-of-grey-sequel-not-directing-1201459967/|website=Variety|publisher=Variety|accessdate=2015-04-27|date=2015-03-25|archive-date=2016-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161129145805/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/sam-taylor-johnson-fifty-shades-of-grey-sequel-not-directing-1201459967/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月22日，公司宣布[[埃里卡·倫納德|埃里卡·倫納德]]的丈夫尼爾·倫納德（Niall Leonard）將會為續集撰寫劇本<ref name=niall>{{cite web|last1=Fleming, Jr.|first1=Mike|script-title=en:Niall Leonard, Husband Of ‘Fifty Shades’ Author, Writing Sequel|url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/niall-leonard-husband-of-fifty-shades-author-writing-sequel-1201414550/|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2015-04-27|date=2015-04-25|archive-date=2016-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329083447/http://deadline.com/2015/04/niall-leonard-husband-of-fifty-shades-author-writing-sequel-1201414550/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月，環球影業的董事長當娜·蘭利（Donna Langley）向《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》透露第二集將會有「更多驚慄元素」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/thr-esq/power-lawyers-donna-langley-fifty-792374|title=Universal's Donna Langley: 'Fifty Shades' Sequel Will Be "More of a Thriller"|first=Austin|last=Siegemund-Broka|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=([[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]])|date=2015-04-29|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2015-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502215851/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/thr-esq/power-lawyers-donna-langley-fifty-792374|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年7月，公司落實了歌手[[瑞塔·奥拉|瑞塔·奥拉]]將返回續集飾演她的角色米婭·格雷<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mahajan|first1=Mradula|script-title=en:‘Fifty Shades Darker’ Movie Cast Updates: Charlize Theron And Henry Cavill Confirmed For Sequel?|url=http://www.movienewsguide.com/fifty-shades-darker-movie-cast-updates-charlize-theron-and-henry-cavill-confirmed-for-sequel/74157|accessdate=2015-07-21|work=movienewsguide.com|date=2015-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171110171835/https://www.movienewsguide.com/fifty-shades-darker-movie-cast-updates-charlize-theron-and-henry-cavill-confirmed-for-sequel/74157|archive-date=2017-11-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2015年8月20日，《死線》透露{{link-en|詹姆斯·佛利 (导演)|James Foley (director)|詹姆斯·佛利}}是電影的領跑員，他將執導續集和第三集的電影。跟詹姆斯·佛利商議前，工作室的其他導演也曾獲考慮，包括{{link-en|麗貝卡·托馬斯|Rebecca Thomas}}、{{link-en|馬克·佩林頓|Mark Pellington}}及{{link-en|譚雅·韋克斯勒|Tanya Wexler}}<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|script-title=en:James Foley Frontrunner To Direct ‘Fifty Shades Of Grey’ Sequel For Universal|url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/james-foley-fifty-shades-of-grey-sequels-fifty-shades-darker-fifty-shades-freed-universal-1201500407/|accessdate=2015-08-21|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2015-08-20|archive-date=2015-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150821115043/http://deadline.com/2015/08/james-foley-fifty-shades-of-grey-sequels-fifty-shades-darker-fifty-shades-freed-universal-1201500407/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年11月12日，娛樂網站TheWrap確認指詹姆斯·佛利將為兩齣續集執導，將會是以背對背的方式拍攝，{{link-en|邁克·德·魯卡|Michael De Luca}}（Michael De Luca）及{{link-en|唐納·布內提|Dana Brunetti}}（Brunetti）將會與[[埃里卡·倫納德|埃里卡·倫納德]]返回製作團隊<ref name=Nov2015TW>{{cite news|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|script-title=en:‘Fifty Shades of Grey’ Sequels to Shoot Back to Back, James Foley to Direct Both (Exclusive)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/fifty-shades-of-grey-sequels-to-shoot-back-to-back-james-foley-to-direct-both-exclusive/|accessdate=2015-11-15|work=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]|date=2015-11-12|archive-date=2015-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151115225127/http://www.thewrap.com/fifty-shades-of-grey-sequels-to-shoot-back-to-back-james-foley-to-direct-both-exclusive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[達珂塔·強生|達珂塔·強生]]與[[傑米·道南|傑米·道南]]都將會返回續集。

